Wide Compatibility - This plug in adapter is compatible with most doorbells on the market, including Ring, Nest, Arlo, Eufy, Wyze and others.

Low Battery Issue is Solved - The adapter is a quick and convenient way to charge your smart doorbells continuously. Now get rid of all battery issues and with no more interrupt or any safety concerns.

Certificated Safe to Use - Made of high quality fireproof material and pure copper plugs. A waterproofed 16.4ft cable is long enough for you to put the doorbell any where higher or lower on your wall.
2 Yrs Warranty - The adapter comes with 10 clips for easy install. 2 Yrs quality warranty. Feel free to contact us if you have any questions.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Use this to connect the Ring doorbell then I got for my parents as a gift. I didn't know they didn't have a wired doorbell connection, so I was looking at having to buy a new product. I was pleasantly surprised to find that the solution was as easy as it is. So much so that I bought another one for my house to connect a doorbell that never had a wired connection. Pretty happy about that.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 20, 2023
reviews.reviewText: We recently moved and the doorbell on the new house doesn't have any power. Rather than fix the doorbell wiring, I bought this to charge my ring doorbell from a nearby outlet. I just plug it in to fully charge the doorbell when needed and then I unplug it because I am not sure how weatherproof it is.
